{
  "id": 5078190552907776,
  "name": "WebAudio: Configurable render quantum",
  "summary": "Adds an optional renderSizeHint to AudioContext and OfflineAudioContext. This allows developers to customize the WebAudio render quantum size by passing a specific integer, use the default of 128 frames by omitting the hint or passing \"default\", or request that the User-Agent select an optimal size by specifying \"hardware\".",
